sequenceDiagram
    participant Anyone as Jeff / Other Role
    participant Slack as Slack Channel
    participant Bridge as Slack Bridge (Docker)
    participant Claude as Claude API (Sonnet)

    loop Every 30 seconds
        Bridge->>Slack: Poll channels
        Slack-->>Bridge: New messages

        alt New message found
            Note over Bridge: Route to appropriate role
            Bridge->>Bridge: Rate limit check

            alt Within rate limit
                Bridge->>Bridge: Assemble context
                Bridge->>Claude: API call (1024 tokens)
                Claude-->>Bridge: Response text
                Bridge->>Slack: Post response + bridge marker
            else Rate limited
                Note over Bridge: Skip
            end
        else No new messages
            Note over Bridge: Sleep until next poll
        end
    end

    Note over Anyone: Jeff sees bridge responses in Slack
